      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.63q7sFrEiOS4UMQ2]{Pistol Dancer}</p>\n<p>You gain a cumulative +2 insight bonus to damage rolls for every previous successful ranged or melee attack with a small arm in the same combat, to a maximum bonus equal to half your soldier level ([[floor(@classes.soldier.levels/2)]]). The bonus doesn’t reset if you miss with an attack, but it does if you didn’t spend the previous round attacking with a small arm.</p>\n<p><em>(You will need to manually increase the damage beyond the 1st application)</em></p>"
